metadata.name: Zeus' Epiphany
metadata.description: Amidst a sea of cool purples and blues, "Zeus' Epiphany" blooms with ethereal flowers, evoking a sense of otherworldly wonder. The flowers seem to dance in the divine glow of the heavens, their delicate petals vibrating with the power of the gods. The artwork hints at the transcendental beauty that lies beyond our mortal vision, urging us to embrace the mysteries of the universe and surrender to the awe-inspiring forces that guide us.
